# Expo Setup & Development

## Project Stack

This is an **Expo** project, not a bare React Native project.

### Why Expo?
- ✅ Easier offline-first with expo-sqlite
- ✅ Simpler build process (no Gradle/Xcode headaches)
- ✅ Better developer experience
- ✅ Works perfectly with Firebase/Firestore
- ✅ Expo Router for navigation

---

## Initial Setup

### Create New Project

```powershell
# Start fresh with Expo
npx create-expo-app@latest

# Choose app name (e.g., "Accounting")
# This creates: C:\Project\Accounting\Accounting\
# Then rename to src: Rename-Item "Accounting" "src"
```

### First Run

```powershell
cd src               # Navigate to Expo project
npm run android      # Opens Android emulator
npm run web          # Opens in browser
npm start            # Shows QR for Expo Go app
```

