## Key Expo Commands

**All commands run from src/ directory:**

```powershell
cd C:\Project\Accounting\src

# Development
npm start                    # Start Metro bundler
npm run android              # Run on Android emulator
npm run web                  # Run in web browser

# Install packages
npx expo install <package>   # Expo-compatible version
npm install <package>        # Standard npm package

# Build
npx expo prebuild            # Generate native folders (android/ios)
eas build --platform android # Build APK/AAB with EAS
```

