## Building for Production

### 1. Install EAS CLI
```powershell
npm install -g eas-cli
eas login
```

### 2. Configure EAS
```powershell
eas build:configure
```

### 3. Build APK
```powershell
# Development build
eas build --profile development --platform android

# Production build
eas build --profile production --platform android
```

